00:42:22,870 --> 00:42:27,350
After a fire, the time it takes for plant life to recover can be as short as a dozen years,

525
00:42:27,350 --> 00:42:29,470
or as long as several decades.

526
00:42:29,470 --> 00:42:36,910
It's a very long process, but it continues to grow even if it looks barren.

527
00:42:36,910 --> 00:42:42,560
One day, it will return to its original lush appearance.

528
00:42:46,270 --> 00:42:47,870
Huan Er.

529
00:42:49,410 --> 00:42:51,120
Sorry.

530
00:42:52,060 --> 00:42:57,180
I shouldn't have lost my temper with you yesterday.

