It seems like we haven't sat together quietly like this for a long time.

535
00:43:24,060 --> 00:43:28,620
In these past few days, I've been thinking...

536
00:43:29,660 --> 00:43:36,220
whether my decision to leave Wuan for Beijing was right or wrong.

537
00:43:39,060 --> 00:43:43,990
It's true that I've been busy this month,

538
00:43:44,990 --> 00:43:50,755
but it's also true that my heart feels empty.

539
00:43:52,790 --> 00:43:55,220
When I was in Wuan,

540
00:43:55,790 --> 00:44:01,040
my favorite thing of the day was to take the subway for half an hour at 6:30 p.m.

541
00:44:02,390 --> 00:44:11,550
and change buses three times, so that I could go across the city to see you.

542
00:44:13,890 --> 00:44:16,140
But after arriving to Beijing,

543
00:44:17,700 --> 00:44:22,370
there's no bus or subway...

544
00:44:24,950 --> 00:44:27,150
that can take me to you.

545
