I feel the same way.

546
00:44:43,220 --> 00:44:47,170
I've already regarded Wuan as my other home.

547
00:44:48,200 --> 00:44:58,500
But since you left, I just feel that even the most familiar places have become unfamiliar.

548
00:45:02,350 --> 00:45:04,180
Chen Huan Er,

549
