do you ever regret being with me?

550
00:45:11,250 --> 00:45:15,570
Have you lost your mind?

551
00:45:17,470 --> 00:45:22,260
Do you know why I'm called Chen Huan Er?

552
00:45:23,760 --> 00:45:26,212
Because I was always hospitalized when I was a kid.

553
00:45:26,212 --> 00:45:27,660
The nurses wouldn't call patients' names.

554
00:45:27,660 --> 00:45:32,390
They only called the patient in bed 3, or the patient in bed 5.

555
00:45:32,390 --> 00:45:37,790
Whenever my mom heard these words, she would be frightened.

556
00:45:37,790 --> 00:45:45,250
 But my mom said since we're stuck with it, we'll try to turn the bad into good. 

557
00:45:46,100 --> 00:45:51,620
That's why those words became my name. 
